<main class="container py-4">
  <div class="p-4 mb-4 bg-body-tertiary rounded-3">
    <div class="container-fluid py-4">
      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Glyph, Info VI</h1>
      <p class="col-md-8 fs-3">
        Glyph is a Discord bot with a powerful starboard system, link embed generation,
        and various other fun features.
      </p>
      <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/config">Config Editor</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/invite">Invite Link</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/server">Support Server</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/source">Source Code</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="d-none">Skills</h2>

  <div class="row row-gap-4 skills" id="skills">
    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">‚≠ê Starboard</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="row row-gap-2">
            <div class="col-md">
              <p class="card-text">
                When configured, Glyph will send messages to a starboard channel when they reach a certain
                threshold of reactions.
                Think of it like democratic pins without limits.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md text-center">
              <img src="/img/starboard.png" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">üëÄ QuickViews</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="row row-gap-2">
            <div class="col-md">
              <p class="card-text">
                Glyph will automatically create improved embeds for links to Fur Affinity and Picarto.
                Post links without needing to remember to add "fx" to them.
                He can even find the Fur Affinity submission if only the image link is given.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md text-center">
              <img src="/img/fa-quickview.png" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">üó®Ô∏è Chat</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">
            Glyph uses DialogFlow to respond to questions you ask.
            He's not a transformer, so don't expect much, but there are some fun surprises.
          </p>
          <samp>How are you?</samp>
          <samp>8 ball</samp>
          <samp>Is 8 NumberWang?</samp>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">üîç Wikis</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">
            Glyph can search Wikipedia and any configured Fandom wikis to quickly research topics.
          </p>
          <samp>Who is Garrus Vakarian according to masseffect wiki?</samp>
          <samp>What are trilobites?</samp>
          <samp>Who is Bill Nye?</samp>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">üí• Moderation</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">
            Glyph can help with moderation tasks, including kicking, banning, and purging chat messages.
          </p>
          <samp>user info for @someone</samp>
          <samp>kick @someone for being rude</samp>
          <samp>ban @someone</samp>
          <samp>purge 3h for spam</samp>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">üë• Roles</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">
            Glyph can assign custom roles to users when configured.
          </p>
          <samp>roles list</samp>
          <samp>make me a Turian</samp>
          <samp>remove me from Geth</samp>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3 class="card-title">‚ùì Server Questions</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">
            Glyph can answer some general questions about your server.
          </p>
          <samp>who is the server owner?</samp>
          <samp>how old is this server?</samp>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
